  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"f-gk9SL1\">我想起来林肯公园《numb》中的一句歌词，tired of being you want me to be</p><p data-pid=\"JoYkatkT\">  我想对你说，just be yourself</p><p data-pid=\"ex0AGojC\">  女生该有女生的样子?三从四德?三纲五常?守妇道?女德?</p><p data-pid=\"5--l8_h6\">  毛线啊（不想骂脏话，然而……）</p><p data-pid=\"8dfy_qRU\">  每个人都有自己的本性啊，又不必一样，做你想做的自己就好，管宿管大妈干嘛?况且，人非圣贤孰能无过</p><p data-pid=\"8I_SDH-x\">  最后还是那句话，just be yourself</p><p data-pid=\"n2BAc0jB\">  顺便邀请下大佬和朋友 </p><span><span class=\"UserLink\"><div class=\"css-1gomreu\"><a class=\"UserLink-link\" data-za-detail-view-element_name=\"User\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"//www.zhihu.com/people/4eaf4607b48c305ffb89508d6bb08587\">@神乐坂千鹤</a></div></span></span><p>  </p><span><span class=\"UserLink\"><div class=\"css-1gomreu\"><a class=\"UserLink-link\" data-za-detail-view-element_name=\"User\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"//www.zhihu.com/people/342772251a575864854652cacf6144fd\">@吧啦</a></div></span></span><p> </p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "我想起来林肯公园《numb》中的一句歌词，tired of being you want me to be\n\n我想对你说，just be yourself\n\n女生该有女生的样子?三从四德?三纲五常?守妇道?女德?\n\n毛线啊（不想骂脏话，然而……）\n\n每个人都有自己的本性啊，又不必一样，做你想做的自己就好，管宿管大妈干嘛?况且，人非圣贤孰能无过\n\n最后还是那句话，just be yourself\n\n顺便邀请下大佬和朋友\n\n@神乐坂千鹤\n\n@吧啦",
